KitKat2::
She looked at DarkMouse and nodded.  DarkMouse got up and left the mess 
hall.  She went up to the bridge and started checking the scanners and 
security systems.
KitKat2 looked at Drillbit. "How I got here? I walked here from the CR tank. 
DarkMouse fixed me up and now I'm here with you. Why do you looked shocked? 
I mean, why wouldn't I be here?" Then she remembered why DarkMouse had told 
her. "Oh, that, well, according to DarkMouse, I was hurt badly from the 
snake bite.  She said I was reborn and now I'm back. Why, what's wrong?"

GoldenEye::
She smirked at Dollen's responce. "Yeah, have a nice nap there pal. I'll be 
out hunting if you need me."

She turned and went to the armory.  She found a nice electron staff and 
started to practice her moves.
